{"tid":1959233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傅振中帶領大批市民代表全港市民心聲向港台示威","createTime":"2020-04-05T09:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T16:23:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ad006ad1121a4524660967a241507c6f7c1e63c5","tid":1959233,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200405/large/1586075754_eba3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200405%2Flarge%2F1586075754_eba3.jpg&h=76920397&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2610f01ac8fa8440971f8adf8378c7b9f8a96dad","tid":1959233,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情爆發，特區政府採取新一輪的抗疫措施，限制4人以上的集會，以減少人流的聚集。親中團體保衞香港運動今午（5日）舉辦集會，抗議早前問及世衞會否重新考慮台灣會員資格的港電節目《The Pulse》記者唐若韞，但團體疑怕違反政府早前推出的「禁聚令」，到場抗議人士僅得4人。<br />\n<br />\n保衞香港運動一行4人以「公然煽惑台獨分裂國家 香港電台快解僱唐若韞」為標語到港台門外示威。發言人傳振中表示，他們今次的集會是「相當守規矩」，只會得4人在港台外示威抗議。他們示威約10分鐘後，便遞交請願信離開。"},{"pid":"1b32aa6e1268ff44264f0b71f7054044ca2970d1","tid":1959233,"uid":160592,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"仆街咁多人點算"},{"pid":"b7e5ebb13733bacf27214eb0d262e8233cee9fb7","tid":1959233,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"Hea爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cbbf7ff09798454059166d84c8315fd5332661","tid":1959233,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1b32aa6e1268ff44264f0b71f7054044ca2970d1","tid":1959233,"uid":160592,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"仆街咁多人點算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"代表沉默大多數市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d2a2e06a492b35b868ba339866009134ad22b8","tid":1959233,"uid":184103,"like":5,"dislik